Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Real Estate
Sub-Industry: REIT
Rich Uncles REIT, Inc. operates as a real estate investment trust. The Company focuses on the investment in single tenant income producing corporate properties. Rich Uncles REIT conducts business in the United States.




